com.google.code.ssm.transcoders
Class JavaTranscoder

java.lang.Object
  com.google.code.ssm.transcoders.JavaTranscoder
All Implemented Interfaces:
CacheTranscoder
public class JavaTranscoder
extends Object
implements CacheTranscoder

Transcoder responsible to decode and encode objects using default java serialization/deserialization. Before storing data if size of data is bigger than defined setCompressionThreshold(int) those data are compressed using GZIP. This transcoder is similar to SerializingTranscoder in xmemcached or spymemcached.

Since:
3.0.0
Author:
Jakub Bia≈Çek
